
====================
Debian/Ubuntu Readme
====================

Note: tested on Ubuntu Oneiric

Package Creation
================

- Install necessary packages
  aptitude install -y git-core python-stdeb debhelper 
  mkdir /var/tmp/deb

- python-cloudfiles
  cd /tmp
  git clone http://github.com/rackspace/python-cloudfiles.git
  cd python-cloudfiles
  python setup.py --command-packages=stdeb.command bdist_deb
  cp /tmp/python-cloudfiles/deb_dist/python-python-cloudfiles_1.7.9.3-1_all.deb /var/tmp/deb

- python-pdflib
  cd /tmp
  wget http://pyftpdlib.googlecode.com/files/pyftpdlib-0.6.0.tar.gz
  tar xzf pyftpdlib-0.6.0.tar.gz
  cd pyftpdlib-0.6.0
  python setup.py --command-packages=stdeb.command bdist_deb
  cp deb_dist/python-pyftpdlib_0.6.0-1_all.deb /var/tmp/deb

- python-ftp-cloudfs
  cd /var/tmp/deb
  dpkg -i python-python-cloudfiles_1.7.9.3-1_all.deb python-pyftpdlib_0.6.0-1_all.deb
  aptitude install -y python-daemon
  apt-file update
  cd /tmp
  git clone http://github.com/chmouel/ftp-cloudfs.git
  cd ftp-cloudfs
  python setup.py --command-packages=stdeb.command bdist_deb
  cp deb_dist/python-ftp-cloudfs_0.9-1_all.deb /var/tmp/deb

- Necessary Package Installation
  dpkg -i /var/tmp/deb/python-ftp-cloudfs_0.9-1_all.deb
  aptitude install -y python-paramiko

- python-sftp-cloudfs
cd /tmp
git clone http://github.com/Memset/sftpcloudfs.git
cd sftpcloudfs
python setup.py --command-packages=stdeb.command bdist_deb
cp /tmp/python-cloudfiles/deb_dist/python-python-cloudfiles_1.7.9.3-1_all.deb /var/tmp/deb
cp /tmp/sftpcloudfs/deb_dist/python-sftp-cloudfs_0.3-1_all.deb /var/tmp/deb

Package Installation
====================

  dpkg -i /var/tmp/deb/python-sftp-cloudfs_0.3-1_all.deb


Configuration
=============


Generate RSA Key File
  
  ssh-keygen -f /etc/sftpcloudfs.key


Minimal example configuration in /etc/sftpcloudfs.conf

***********************************************************
[sftpcloudfs]

# Authentication URL (eg RackSpace Cloud Files, OpenStack)
# auth-url = (empty)
auth-url = https://192.168.100.10/auth/v1.0

# Host RSA key used by the server.
# host-key-file = (empty)
host-key-file = /etc/sftpcloudfs.key

# Address to bind.
# bind-address = 127.0.0.1
bind-address = 0.0.0.0
***********************************************************


Package Log Files
====================

By default, debian package is configured to use logfiles, be aware of it.
Note: Have a look at /etc/init.d/python-sftp-cloudfs
